{"tid":551821,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(先知、智者、富豪) 燈神指路，萬事大吉","createTime":"2018-02-06T03:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T15:56:19.000Z","uid":54337,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49cc0b6c44863128a80dbb2bebc5aa4418d2278b","tid":551821,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:57:49.000Z","msg":"某某人曾經指出：<br />\n<br />\n1) 香港樓市會爆破。但錯撚哂。<br />\n事實係，樓市升到上火星。<br />\n<br />\n2) 香港股市長遠會死。但可惜又錯撚哂。<br />\n事實係，恒指曾經升到三萬二、三萬三千點。<br />\n<br />\n3) 香港會進入大失業時代，裁員潮又湧現。但可惜又錯撚哂。<br />\n事實係，香港乜事都無，無失業裁員潮。<br />\n<br />\n4) 英國不會脫歐。但可惜又錯撚哂。<br />\n事實係，英國脫歐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻過街老鼠、跳樑小丑，無人理會，不甘寂寞，今日又蒲頭。<br />\n<br />\n今日恒指跌千四點。<br />\n各位股友，可以稍安無躁。<br />\n因為某某人又開金口：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/115356_3926f12e7e805e65b2d0d5d88b1df7bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F115356_3926f12e7e805e65b2d0d5d88b1df7bc.png&h=bfa548af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據某某人嘅過去預測記錄，今後恒指會點，大家心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75268f3703b25e2f9523b05fb761da9b70b6ca18","tid":551821,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"( 先知 智者 富豪 )屈機男三大精妙高論回顧<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/216069/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/216069/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"17f2c7e6d5504f01709339343fd1e0392cbdd1a9","tid":551821,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:15:26.000Z","msg":"大家唔使驚，定啲嚟"},{"pid":"98a55c7a62a6da95a1e57da3dd453f070b883efd","tid":551821,"uid":136727,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"有人要針了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實佢做看更<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4966b7ac61e4ff23cfe44fc59c06bca3844e3772","tid":551821,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:44:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5ee8f2b37ed410b1afe6b63aeb167738123de6","tid":551821,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"已block 7<br />\nBtw, 沈陣營推爆左，邊位師兄開返？"},{"pid":"64349d4a19940b2476e647b9a4836ad3a0dff3e7","tid":551821,"uid":33712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250d1446242b1f4e0bee3829f099a11b53dbc8a7","tid":551821,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T09:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb0a84be015f6adf326ce94b1e3c3afb8cebce3","tid":551821,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>被人踢爆扮有錢佬, 敗走高登後. 諗住去連登再扮有錢佬, 點知...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實屈機男現實是咪矮柒毒? <br />\n<br />\n03:06AM 仲見佢連登開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇舊post睇下</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>有冇簡介<br />\n係咪上次吹到好勁一開波就捐錢點知比人反cup個2個</blockquote><br />\n劇情回顧:<br />\n屈機男在高登常以有錢佬姿態教化高登仔做人道理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0i1Q28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0i1Q28.jpg&h=c884d968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈機男常自稱有幾個物業, 但又睇淡樓市<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1Bp683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1Bp683.jpg&h=14ab5e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69n6byc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69n6byc.jpg&h=508c64cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈機男以高高在上姿態雄霸財經台, 而且有一眾信眾追隨.<br />\n然而, 直至會員 米已成炊出現, 他質疑屈機男之有錢言論, 多次挑戰其財經台權威.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3u76373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3u76373.jpg&h=476a844a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是大發明家屈機男發明了解決糾紛方法...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ly869i3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLy869i3.jpg&h=be0daf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/009PHw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F009PHw5.jpg&h=dcad78a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屈機男及其信眾一直強勢, 欺侮米已成炊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKrCVnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKrCVnV.jpg&h=33bd4d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgX65WO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgX65WO.jpg&h=c0ddb46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVg6J3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVg6J3M.jpg&h=f50358a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都係直接飛到結局.... 屈機男捐唔起錢認輸, 而其信眾亦鳥獸散或深潛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6d859G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6d859G.jpg&h=bb060f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw1pgUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw1pgUy.jpg&h=7c7dbc8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8NL1v6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8NL1v6.png&h=401336d2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>屈機男縮撚番佢老母個閪度</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6685702156fa738c34a2c77952e84ca7b19bbf","tid":551821,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a29415ab3c07a4a1ebb61aecd8d072302ff9493","tid":551821,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e36df1c51270bef9c69c79368f041927916a613","tid":551821,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27761aea7ab7f7a80738a45334ace8422e633dfc","tid":551821,"uid":22422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:55:45.000Z","msg":"歷史會話畀大家聽<br />\n師父同船嘅人<br />\n將會落得乜嘢下場<br />\neg 219 信念閪 天閪"},{"pid":"46786b1d9918c2eb3e72ee7cb21abea7eb41018e","tid":551821,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}